violations.description:
Inline lambda braces use K&R style: `page.Console += (_, msg) => {
    if (msg.Type == "error") {
        errors.Add(msg.Text);
    }
};`. The project's `.editorconfig` mandates Allman braces (new line before opening brace). Same K&R-style block appears in Dw5TypeCatalogNavigationBrowserAtddTests.cs:58-62. Other lambdas in the codebase (e.g., `BrowserSmokeTests.cs:14`) use single-line expression-bodied form, and standalone blocks use Allman.
